# @wayofmono/wo-ai

A unified LLM API layer with automatic model discovery and provider configuration.

## Installation

```bash
pnpm add @wayofmono/wo-ai
```

## Features

- **Multi-Provider Support**: Seamlessly switch between OpenAI, Anthropic, Bedrock, Mistral, and Google Gemini.
- **Unified Interface**: Use a consistent API regardless of the underlying LLM provider.
- **Automatic Discovery**: Discovers available models and capabilities automatically.
- **OAuth Support**: Built-in support for OAuth-based authentication where applicable.

## Supported Providers

- OpenAI
- Anthropic
- AWS Bedrock
- Google Gemini
- Mistral AI
